类 Question

  • java.lang.Object
    • bean.Question

  • public class Question
extends Object
    CREATE TABLE `questions` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `big_question` int(11) NOT NULL, `question` varchar(100) NOT NULL, `answer` varchar(100) NOT NULL, `image` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL, `audio` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`), UNIQUE KEY `idquestions_UNIQUE` (`id`), KEY `big_question_idx` (`big_question`), CONSTRAINT `big_question` FOREIGN KEY (`big_question`) REFERENCES `big_question` (`id`) ON DELETE NO ACTION ON UPDATE NO ACTION ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=21 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COMMENT='小题'
